Symbol.Script_VL:
hideparameter all
hideparameter "ZZYZX"
! --- Bottom, Top Level Calculation ---
dim xDistFromCenter[] dim zDistFromCenter[] dim spotRad[] dim alpha[]
xDistFromCenter[1] = 0.083 zDistFromCenter[1] = 0.0355 xDistFromCenter[2] = 0.08 zDistFromCenter[2] = 0.048 xDistFromCenter[3] = 0.0799 zDistFromCenter[3] = 0.0481 xDistFromCenter[4] = 0.055 zDistFromCenter[4] = 0.05 xDistFromCenter[5] = -0.055 zDistFromCenter[5] = 0.0246
for i = 1 to 5 spotRad[i] = SQR(xDistFromCenter[i]**2 + zDistFromCenter[i]**2) alpha[i] = ACS(xDistFromCenter[i] / spotRad[i]) put -spotRad[i] * SIN(alpha[i] - rx) - 0.155 next i
ac_bottomlevel = MIN(GET(nsp)) ac_toplevel = 0 parameters ac_bottomlevel = ac_bottomlevel, ac_toplevel = ac_toplevel
